- use lucide react for the icons
- use bun as package manager
- use shadcn components. install them with bun like so: bunx --bun shadcn@latest add <component>
- no need to use your own colors. respect globals.css
- use tanstack query for fetching data and calling mutations
- write queries in lib/db/queries.ts file and mutations in lib/db/mutations.ts file
- use drizzle-orm's relational api for queries
